    "headline": "Trimble (TRMB) Q1 2026 Earnings Transcript",
    "summary": "The Trimble team furthered the momentum of the last couple of years and delivered a great start to the year, with top and bottom line results ahead of expectations.  On Slide 4, I want to highlight how we are partnering with our customer, George Leslie, a Scottish based civil engineering contractor that has embraced the Trimble ecosystem to connect the physical and digital worlds.  With our platform, Trimble Connect acts as the orchestration layer of complex workflows, that include marine and peer works, water and wastewater treatment, bridges and infrastructure and energy and power.",
